   |url=http://shop.nationalgeographic.com/ngs/product/books/kids-books-and-atlases/animals-and-nature/witness-to-disaster%3A-tsunamis}}
</ref> Galombang nan tingginyo bapuluah meter dapek timbua dek karano bancano alam gadang. Sungguahpun dampak tsunami tabateh ka wilayah pasisia, tanago parusaknyo bisa jadi lua biaso dan dapek mampangaruahi tapian samudra kasadonyo. [[Gampo dan tsunami Samudra Hindia 2004|Tsunami Samudra Hindia 2004]] marupoan salah satu bancano alam paliang mamatian dek sijarah umaik manusia, nan manalan labiah dari 230.000 korban maningga di 14 nagara nan di sakuliliang [[Samudra Hindia]].

Ahli sijarah [[Yunani Kuno]] [[Thucydides]] mampakiroan dalam karyanyo ''[[Sijarah Parang Peloponnesia]]'' nan ditulih pado akia abaik ka-5 SM, bahaso tsunami ko ado kaitannyo jo [[gampo bawah lauik]],<ref name="Thucydides 3.89.1-4">Thucydides: [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/cgi-bin/ptext?lookup=Thuc.+3.89.1 “A History of the Peloponnesian War”, 3.89.1–4]</ref><ref name="Smid, T. C. 103f.">{{cite book|last=Smid|first=T. C.|title='Tsunamis' in Greek Literature|edition=2nd|volume=17|date=April , 1970|pages=100–104|work=Greece & Rome|issue=1}}</ref> tapi pamahaman tantang apo tsunami tu tatap kabua inggo masuak abaik ka-20 walaupun masih banyak pulo nan indak dikataui. Bidang-bidang utamo panalitian kini ko di antaronyo iolah mancubo mangataui baa babarapo gampo gadang indak maasiaan tsunami samantaro nan labiah ketek manyabaukannyo; sarato usao untuak sacaro tapek mampakiroan jalua malintehnyo tsunami di lautan; dan caro mampakiroan baa galombang tsunami ka bapangaruah pado bantuak garih pantai tatantu.

